Data Cleaning and Preprocessing – Handle missing values, encode categorical variables.
Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA) – Analyze churn rates, customer demographics, and tenure distribution.
Customer Segmentation – Segment customers based on tenure, charges, contract type, and analyze churn rates.
Churn Prediction Model – Develop a machine learning model (e.g., Logistic Regression) and evaluate performance.
Customer Retention Strategies – Propose strategies to reduce churn, identify high-value customers at risk.
Visualizations – Create meaningful visualizations (box plots, violin plots, etc.) using tools like Matplotlib or Seaborn.

Key Skills Required
Data Cleaning & Preprocessing
EDA & Visualization (Matplotlib, Seaborn, Tableau)
Machine Learning (Python, R, Logistic Regression)
Customer Segmentation & Retention Strategies
Business Acumen & Analytical Thinking
